\c 7  
\s1 Parenthesis  
\s2 The sealed of Israel  
\m
\v 1 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w after|strong="G3326"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w*\f + \fr 7:1 \ft He saw the content of chapter seven after he saw the content of chapter six, but the events described are not necessarily in chronological order. It should not be assumed that nothing else happened between the seals, or even at the same time. However, the seals are broken in sequence.\f* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w saw|strong="G3708"\w* \w four|strong="G5064"\w* angels \w standing|strong="G2476"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w four|strong="G5064"\w* \w corners|strong="G1137"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*,\f + \fr 7:1 \ft The Text says “\+nd the\+nd* four corners” and “\+nd the\+nd* four winds”. Presumably from John's perspective the earth would look like a sphere (or a circle)—so perhaps the angels were strategically placed so as to control the whole planet. There \+nd are\+nd* four basic wind patterns that influence most of the world—the north and south ‘trade winds’ and the north and south ‘prevailing westerlies’.\f* \w holding|strong="G2902"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w four|strong="G5064"\w* winds \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*, \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w no|strong="G3361"\w* \w wind|strong="G4154"\w* \w should|strong="G3588"\w* \w blow|strong="G4154"\w* \w upon|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*, \w nor|strong="G3383"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sea|strong="G2281"\w*, \w nor|strong="G3383"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w any|strong="G3956"\w* \w tree|strong="G1186"\w*.  
\v 2 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G3739"\w* \w saw|strong="G3708"\w* \w another|strong="G3739"\w* angel ascending \w from|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sun|strong="G2246"\w*'\w s|strong="G2192"\w* \w rising|strong="G2532"\w*, \w having|strong="G2192"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w seal|strong="G4973"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w Living|strong="G2198"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*. \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w cried|strong="G2896"\w* \w out|strong="G2896"\w* \w with|strong="G2532"\w* \w a|strong="G2192"\w* \w loud|strong="G3173"\w* \w voice|strong="G5456"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w four|strong="G5064"\w* angels, \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w whom|strong="G3739"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w had|strong="G2192"\w* \w been|strong="G2192"\w* \w granted|strong="G1325"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* harm \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sea|strong="G2281"\w*,  
\v 3 \w saying|strong="G3004"\w*: “\w Do|strong="G3004"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* harm \w the|strong="G1909"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*, \w nor|strong="G3383"\w* \w the|strong="G1909"\w* \w sea|strong="G2281"\w* \w nor|strong="G3383"\w* \w the|strong="G1909"\w* \w trees|strong="G1186"\w*, until \w we|strong="G2249"\w* \w have|strong="G1473"\w* \w sealed|strong="G4972"\w* \w the|strong="G1909"\w* \w slaves|strong="G1401"\w* \w of|strong="G2316"\w* \w our|strong="G2316"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w their|strong="G3588"\w* \w foreheads|strong="G3359"\w*.”  
\v 4 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* heard \w the|strong="G2532"\w* number \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w were|strong="G3588"\w* \w sealed|strong="G4972"\w*, \w one|strong="G3956"\w* \w hundred|strong="G1540"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w forty|strong="G5062"\w* \w four|strong="G5064"\w* \w thousand|strong="G5505"\w*, \w sealed|strong="G4972"\w* \w out|strong="G1537"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w every|strong="G3956"\w* \w tribe|strong="G5443"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sons|strong="G5207"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w Israel|strong="G2474"\w*:   
\q1
\v 5 \w From|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G1537"\w* \w tribe|strong="G5443"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w Judah|strong="G2455"\w* \w twelve|strong="G1427"\w* \w thousand|strong="G5505"\w* were \w sealed|strong="G4972"\w*,  
\q2 \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G1537"\w* \w tribe|strong="G5443"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w Reuben|strong="G4502"\w* \w twelve|strong="G1427"\w* \w thousand|strong="G5505"\w*,  
