\v 19 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w temple|strong="G3485"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w heaven|strong="G3772"\w* \w was|strong="G1096"\w* opened, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w ark|strong="G2787"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w covenant|strong="G1242"\w*\f + \fr 11:19 \ft Presumably this is the original ark of which the one made under Moses' supervision was a copy (Hebrews 8:5, Exodus 25:9, 40, Hebrews 9:23).\f* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Lord|strong="G3588"\w* \w was|strong="G1096"\w* \w seen|strong="G3708"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w His|strong="G1722"\w* \w temple|strong="G3485"\w*. \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w were|strong="G3588"\w* lightnings, noises, \w thunderings|strong="G1027"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w huge|strong="G3173"\w* \w hail|strong="G5464"\w*.\f + \fr 11:19 \ft If this were all there was to the seventh trumpet it would be anti climactic, ‘small potatoes’. I take it that the seven ‘bowls’ (see chapter 16) give the full content of the third woe.\f*   
