\s2 Satan excluded from heaven  
\p
\v 7 \w War|strong="G4171"\w* \w was|strong="G1096"\w* declared \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w heaven|strong="G3772"\w*; \w Michael|strong="G3413"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w his|strong="G1722"\w* angels \w were|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w wage|strong="G4170"\w* \w war|strong="G4171"\w* \w with|strong="G3326"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w dragon|strong="G1404"\w*; \w so|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w dragon|strong="G1404"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w his|strong="G1722"\w* angels \w made|strong="G1096"\w* \w war|strong="G4171"\w*,\f + \fr 12:7 \ft The dragon knew that Michael had received the order, so he decided to get in the first blow.\f*  
