\c 16  
\m
\v 1 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* heard \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w loud|strong="G3173"\w* \w voice|strong="G5456"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sanctuary|strong="G3485"\w* \w saying|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w seven|strong="G2033"\w* angels, “\w Go|strong="G5217"\w*, \w pour|strong="G1632"\w* \w out|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w bowls|strong="G5357"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*'s fury \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*.”   
\s2 The \nd first\nd* bowl  
\p
\v 2 \w So|strong="G2532"\w* off \w went|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w first|strong="G4413"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w poured|strong="G1632"\w* \w out|strong="G1632"\w* \w his|strong="G1519"\w* \w bowl|strong="G5357"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w earth|strong="G1093"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w a|strong="G2192"\w* foul \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w malignant|strong="G4190"\w* ulcer\f + \fr 16:2 \ft Even now a chip the size of a grain of rice is being planted under the skin of volunteers. The battery contains a substance that, if it leaks out of the chip, will produce “a foul and malignant ulcer”. Notice that ‘ulcer’ is singular, one per person, precisely those who have the ‘mark’. A word to the wise…\f* \w appeared|strong="G1096"\w* \w in|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w people|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w had|strong="G2192"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w mark|strong="G5480"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w beast|strong="G2342"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w worshiped|strong="G4352"\w* \w his|strong="G1519"\w* \w image|strong="G1504"\w*.   
