\v 21 \w The|strong="G3956"\w* \w grace|strong="G5485"\w* \w of|strong="G5485"\w* \w the|strong="G3956"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G2962"\w*\f + \fr 22:21 \ft “The Lord Jesus Christ” is now the full name or title of Jehovah the Son.\f* \w be|strong="G3956"\w* \w with|strong="G3326"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w the|strong="G3956"\w* saints. Amen.   